title: Florence Zeitingale 5/27: Disney World, BurgerKingIsOver, John Boyega, SpaceX
itunes:title: Florence Zeitingale 5/27: Disney World, BurgerKingIsOver, John Boyega, SpaceX
description:
On this edition of Florence Zeitingale Jack and Miles discuss Disney World planning to reopen mid July, Burger King is cancelled because of the way they replied to a question about Taylor Swift, John Boyega said "fuck racists" and people on twitter came for him (?!), and SpaceX WAS set to launch its first manned mission today (but scrubbed due to weather).
